data.description: Don't look any further! You have found your new home. This recently updated home has it all from top to bottom. New 4 piece appliance package, granite countertop, new cabinets, new roof and gutters (2023), windows (2022) recessed lights in vaulted living room and kitchen, new lighting in all rooms, programmable thermostats, new vinyl plank flooring in kitchen and lower level family room, both bathrooms updated, and new garage door. Hardwood flooring in all bedrooms, hallway and living/dining room.
